Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照射黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.43,0:00:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說 促使宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.34,0:00:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.31,0:00:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方 呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.79,0:00:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.76,0:00:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.36,0:00:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.80,0:00:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.18,0:00:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.19,0:00:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.96,0:01:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.73,0:01:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百分之十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.33,0:01:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.56,0:01:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果使用依您的要求\N所設計出的無人操縱功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.27,0:01:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超重幽靈系統」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.80,0:01:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神的戰鬥力\N將會下降百分之十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.77,0:01:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只犧牲掉這點程度就可以的話\N那就真是相當理想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.74,0:01:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你了 朵利雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.48,0:02:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我把愛灌注其中的\N自信大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.09,0:02:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點進行最終調整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.09,0:02:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等G戰騎回來後 進行測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.06,0:02:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙他們出去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟生活班一起出去買東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪這麼安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十話龜裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啦...\N能夠到街上來 是很高興啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N為什麼我們的成員是這樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是一群手無縛雞之力的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.83,0:03:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我、我來幫忙提一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用、不用...妳提不動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦\N人家老是造成您的困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起碼這點小事總該...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點撿起來快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.24,0:03:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...對不起\N我真是的又給您添麻煩了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦妳不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子 真的能見到綾香嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙你看、你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠好可愛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.93,0:04:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓬蓬的好想養喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向朵利雅要求的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會幫你做一隻\N一模一樣的機械貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這你就不懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.34,0:04:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想養這隻活生生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙你也抱抱看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙那邊沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.99,0:04:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小子\N從小就生活在城堡裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.46,0:04:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是不點不靈嘛..\N還是該說他沒見過世面...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.17,0:04:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有琉菜小姐陪著他嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.30,0:04:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜 妳啊...斗牙和琉菜這麼親密\N妳難道都沒有什麼感覺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.18,0:04:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.18,0:04:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也喜歡斗牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.85,0:04:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.78,0:04:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也好喜歡琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也喜歡琉菜小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:05:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以看他們倆個相親相愛的\N我也感到很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像也有哪裡少根筋呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真乖呢 雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看!斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎..怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是雷文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上到在現場的G要塞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.76,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到達之後 G戰騎跟要塞會合\N立刻出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.61,0:06:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種把大樓的瓦礫\N裹覆在自己身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.91,0:07:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是為了\N讓自己更堅固以利作戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我保養維修好的超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經足以突破\N那種程度的裝甲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢測出外星異種內部有Θ射線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.46,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體內似乎擁有素粒子破壞系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要受到Θ射線照射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半徑一百公里範圍內的生物\N都會死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概1800秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.58,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1800秒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...那麼...\N不就只剩30分鐘!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.98,0:08:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露!我去救她!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.90,0:08:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.73,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上會帶雪希露回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們就留在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露! 愛娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺、琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.65,0:09:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露!妳在哪?雪希露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找雪希露了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 還說會馬上回來的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.11,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜 總之我們也過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 遵命 琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...雪希露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡?雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.05,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜 還有多少時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.33,0:10:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1000秒...不到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.11,0:10:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Θ射線開始照射時間是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩987秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.82,0:11:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是當外星異種\N完全變白的時候就會發射出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.93,0:11:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵利雅\N幽靈系統已經組裝完畢了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 全好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能完美的運作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙 發動工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下再讓英司和你們會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少了英司的合神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.91,0:11:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個幽靈系統吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經合神了?我又不在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神合神完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G攻擊機 幽靈系統運作正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.58,0:13:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!成功了!順利運作了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好、好痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 快到安全區域裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓G要塞去接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是雪希露她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重來福槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近不了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 你想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去救雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前\N就先自己作戰 拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太胡來了!英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離重力子臨界點還有4879點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.49,0:14:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離Θ射線照射時間\N還剩597秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼 沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打都打不完嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.42,0:15:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點還有3233點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左側重鑽駕駛艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重龍捲拳\N發射預備!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙你想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想對雪希露攻擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我救她出來前\N你先等著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備完成後立刻發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.14,0:15:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊接著使用超重新月鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.31,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確...是應該要把損害\N減輕到最低可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗、斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙 不要發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你聽到了沒\N快回答我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺\N真的打算對雪希露射擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.80,0:16:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離Θ射線照射時間\N還剩398秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點還有2985點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.88,0:16:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重鑽機駕駛艙 重戰影駕駛艙\N妳們在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.92,0:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司也在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點還有2533點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.15,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Θ射線照射時間還剩297秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到5分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺 別發射呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手呀!斗牙!不要射擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.11,0:17:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清醒點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.75,0:17:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.17,0:17:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Θ射線照射時間57秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍捲旋風拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍捲旋風拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Θ射線照射時間 14秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.99,0:19:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.01,0:20:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這麼問我也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的任務\N就是要打倒外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就可以什麼都不管了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了雪希露也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.56,0:20:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣還算是人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.79,0:20:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起外星異種\N你這混蛋還更像個怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.11,0:20:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.44,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙也以他的方式\N做了最佳的考量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓同伴死掉\N能叫做最佳考量嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不幹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和這種混蛋在一起\N誰受得了啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司\N英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.76,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是在計畫中的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.75,0:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.26,0:21:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.44,0:21:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.01,0:22:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.62,0:22:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.63,0:22:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.16,0:22:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.00,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.84,0:22:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.11,0:22:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.65,0:22:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.35,0:22:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.36,0:22:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.13,0:22:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到英司少爺...\N真的離開城堡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.17,0:22:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.14,0:22:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.21,0:22:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.44,0:23:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出\N"失去的事物"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.48,0:23:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週 我們也將會照料各位的和平!